layout.markdownText: As a **Fleet Operator** I want to understand the SoH of different fleets, do aging analysis, so that I can understand and benchmark aging of fleets with different driving + environment conditions which will help me plan replacements and understand any performance deterioration (e.g.range decline)

Electric Vehicle Battery Aging is influenced by multiple factors like **temperature, mileage, geography**, along with this, it is also affected by the **usage behavior of the driver:** how they drive : driving profile , what intensity are the batteries charged and discharged etc.

Here, we are trying to understand and access **Aging patterns** with different driving conditions
- Fleet 2 operating at high temperature regions with aggressive driving conditions
- Fleet 3 operating at average temperature with some driving conditions like high speeds + acceleration
- Fleet 1 and 4 operating with an average driving condition/style and comparatively lower temperature

This dashboard is based on **Internal SoH Semi-Empirical Model**
